        <id>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reine_Audu</id>
        <link href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reine_Audu"/>
        <updated>2026-07-14T07:26:00.196Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[... that the fruit seller <b><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reine_Audu" title="Reine Audu">Reine Audu</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i> was jailed after the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Women's_March_on_Versailles" title="Women's March on Versailles">march on Versailles in 1789</a> for announcing her intention to "[bring] back the Queen's head on her sword", among other charges?]]></content>
